---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Maria Golia International Piano Competition">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">About the Competition</h1>

      <div class="content">
        <p class="intro">
          The Maria Golia International Piano Competition is a prestigious event dedicated to discovering and promoting
          young pianistic talent from around the world.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Named in honor of Maria Golia, a passionate advocate for music education, this competition aims to provide
          a platform for emerging pianists to showcase their abilities and launch their international careers.
        </p>

        <h2>The Competition</h2>
        <p>
          Taking place in the magnificent setting of the Castello Ducale di Agli√® in Piedmont, Italy, the competition
          offers participants the unique experience of performing in one of Italy's most beautiful Baroque residences.
        </p>
        <p>
          The competition is divided into two sections: Youth Categories for pianists up to 18 years old, and the
          International Section for pianists aged 18-32, featuring substantial cash prizes and concert opportunities.
        </p>

        <h2>Artistic Direction</h2>
        <p>
          Under the artistic direction of Marina Scalafiotti, the competition brings together an international jury
          of distinguished pianists and pedagogues to evaluate participants.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 750px;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
